These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-1::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: chess, reading, singing, sudoku, video-games
There are 5 different favourite colors: red, ebony, grey, coral, fuchsia
1. the person who's hobby is reading is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##5
5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1
6. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
7. the person who likes coral is somewhere to the right of the person who likes red##5
8. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |      3       |    4    |     5      |
| Hobby   | chess    | video-games   | reading      | sudoku  | singing    |
| Color   | red | fuchsia | grey | ebony | coral |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-2::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: action, animation, documentary, musical, spy
There are 5 different favourite colors: red, turquise, yellow, purple, white
 1. the person who likes yellow is somewhere to the right of the person watching action movies##5
 2. the person who likes white is somewhere to the right of the person who likes red##5
 3. the person who likes red is somewhere to the right of the person who likes purple##5
 4. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
 5. the person who likes white is somewhere to the left of the person who likes yellow##5
 6. the person who likes red is on the left or right of the person who likes white##3
 7. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
 8. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3
 9. the person watching animation movies is in the middle##1
10. the person watching animation movies is between the person who likes purple and the person who likes white##2
11. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching musical movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |      4      |   5    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical   | action     | animation | documentary | spy    |
| Color     | turquise | purple | red   | white        | yellow |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-3::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: swimming, skateboarding, water-polo, basketball, weightlifting
The people have 5 different hobbies: board-games, card-games, dancing, gardening, reading
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person who's sport is swimming##1
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##5
7. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
8. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who's sport is swimming##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |
| Sport   | water-polo   | skateboarding       | weightlifting         | swimming | basketball |
| Hobby      | dancing | card-games | board-games | gardening   | reading |

