.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-4::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: camping, filmmaking, gardening, hiking, drawing
There are 5 different nationalities: british, canadian, indonesian, italian, russian
 1. the russian is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
 2. the british is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is the italian##1
 4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 5. the italian is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 6. the british is on the left or right of the canadian##3
 7. the canadian is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 8. the canadian is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an odd position##4
10. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |    4     |     5      |
| Hobby   | hiking     | gardening  | drawing   | filmmaking      | camping  |
| Nationality   | italian | russian | british | canadian | indonesian |

