.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-5::.
There 5 different types of food: artichoke, cabbage, papaya, pear, radish
5 different games are played: domino, poker, snooker, mah-jongg, whist
1. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person eating artichoke##3
2. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
3. the person playing snooker is between the person eating radish and the person playing poker##2
4. the person eating pear is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
5. the person playing domino is somewhere to the left of the person eating papaya##5
6. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
7. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |   5    |
| Food    | cabbage | artichoke | papaya     | pear     | radish |
| Game   | whist  | domino   | poker | snooker | mah-jongg |

