.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-7::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, juice, milk, soy-milk
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, baseball, surfing, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
5. the person drinking milk is the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is surfing##5
7. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##5
8. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |   2   |   3   |     4     |   5   |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | milk  | fanta | soy-milk  | juice |
| Sport   | lacrosse          | baseball | surfing | badminton | cricket   |

