.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-8::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: subway, helicopter, ship, skateboard, quad-bike
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, australian, canadian, italian, nigerian
1. the person driving the subway is the person driving the subway##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the nigerian##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the nigerian is on the right of the australian##1
6. the argentine is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5
7. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person driving the subway and the italian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5     |
| Transport          | ship    | helicopter    | quad-bike | subway | skateboard   |
| Nationality   | canadian | italian | australian | nigerian  | argentine |

