.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-11::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: cola, lemonade, milk, mirinda, tea
There 5 different types of food: orange, grapes, eggplant, lime, pineapple
 1. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 2. the person eating orange is in an even position##4
 3. the person eating orange is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3
 4. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person eating orange##3
 5. the person eating lime is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
 7. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
 8. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the right of the person eating pineapple##5
 9. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking cola and the person drinking mirinda##2
10. the person eating pineapple is somewhere to the left of the person eating grapes##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |    4    |    5     |
| Beverage   | tea     | cola       | milk    | mirinda | lemonade |
| Food      | pineapple | grapes | eggplant | orange | lime  |

