.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-13::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, lemonade, soy-milk, sprite, tea
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, baccarat, dunhill, tiparillo, ritmeester
1. the person drinking sprite is between the chaman-smoker and the person drinking tea##2
2. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3
3. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
5. the dunhill-smoker is somewhere to the left of the ritmeester-smoker##5
6. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
7. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
8. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere to the left of the baccarat-smoker##5
9. the baccarat-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4      |   5    |
| Beverage    | tea        | sprite | soy-milk | lemonade   | coffee |
| Cigar   | dunhill | ritmeester  | chaman     | baccarat | tiparillo  |

