.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-14::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  accountant, librarian, teacher, videographer, writer
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: baseball, water-polo, lacrosse, parkour, tennis
1. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the right of the teacher##5
2. the accountant is between the teacher and the person who's sport is lacrosse##2
3. the writer is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is parkour##5
4. the accountant is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3
6. the person who's sport is parkour is in an even position##4
7. the librarian is the person who's sport is parkour##1
8. the person who's sport is baseball is the accountant##1
9. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person who's sport is parkour and the accountant##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |    5    |
| Job   | videographer | accountant | teacher    | librarian | writer  |
| Sport   | lacrosse       | baseball       | water-polo | parkour  | tennis |

