.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-16::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: hiking, magic-tricks, singing, skydiving, traveling
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: drama, musical, scientific, zombie, disaster
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in the middle##1
2. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
