4. the person watching drama movies is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
5. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left##1
6. the person watching disaster movies is the person who's hobby is singing##1
7. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1
8. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the person watching zombie movies##5
9. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3       |     4     |    5    |
| Hobby         | hiking  | traveling | magic-tricks | skydiving | singing |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | scientific   | musical   | drama | disaster |

