4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
5. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
6. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5
7. the owner of the guinea-pig is in the middle##1
8. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |
| Beverage      | milk      | iced-tea | mirinda | sprite    | lemonade  |
| Pet   | snake | bird   | guinea-pig | turtle | dog |

