.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-20::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, juice, milk, soy-milk
There are 5 different favourite colors: fuchsia, blood-red, pink, azure, apricot
1. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking soy-milk##2
2. the person who likes fuchsia is between the person who likes pink and the person drinking fanta##2
3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
4. the person who likes apricot is somewhere to the right of the person who likes blood-red##5
5. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
6. the person who likes azure is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |      2       |     3      |      4       |    5     |
| Beverage   | milk      | soy-milk     | fanta      | coffee       | juice    |
| Color        | pink | fuchsia | blood-red | apricot | azure |

 